Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why is it only when one loses something,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:49.35,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Nee hito wa itsumo nani ka nakushita toki ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:57.66,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Ari no mama no jibun ni kidzuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets to perceive what was actually going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wonder if you can hear me \Neven while you're not here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:05.67,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Nee ima wa inai anata kikoeru kashira
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made a promise to carry on living my own way, \Ntherefore you must also, even if for an eternity,
