Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hitting the road \Nto see Jin's favourite Sea of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now free.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I finally let go of racket, \NI found freedom in these hands{maybe it'd be more prudent to say "in this heart/body" seeing as she points to it while speaking; also, I'm not even sure it's "hands" cause there's a dime a dozen meanings for "te"}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This leaves me with plenty of time \NI can spend thinking of Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't quit playing.{/let go of your racket.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to see you one day{/at least once more} \Nhitting that cannon serve again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure is one of the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike you, \NI cannot live off{/fuel my life with} tennis only.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Jin bequeathed his sardonic tone{/sharp/straightforward tongue} to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin, the way you saw it, the way you felt it, \NI want to feel{ and see} it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That sea is among the few things \Nthat grant me momentarily tranquility.{/brings peace into my mind like nothing else.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The lives{/memories/experience} of people from bygone ages \Nare sealed{/preserved/frozen/immortalized} in it{ entirely/in full}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At a moment's notice,{guess; all I really heard is "fukkari namariyori no to the bottom drag", everything before it is a guesswork; I assumed fukkari to be a twisted sukkari} \Nit can drag you all the way to the seabed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin...
