Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At such a late{/advanced} {disease }development stage, it's but a miracle{/mystery to us how} \Nhe was able to lead a physically active{/healthy/carefree} life up{/all the way} until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Three more years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the cutting-edge medical advancements\Ncannot grant him more than that.{/Even applying our utmost(it's more like "over the top") medical effort/treatment, we cannot guarantee that he lasts any longer than that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It pains me to inform you.{/I'm sorry to tell you this.}
